{"tid":550062,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"毒 男 坤 哥 IG 晒 與 鬼 妹 合 照","createTime":"2018-02-04T10:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T10:59:23.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"029ad4f4816f301556c61f268599a510d0aa74fd","tid":550062,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"吳業坤（坤哥）經常被指係食女無數嘅「偽毒」，近日更越級同薛家燕傳「緋聞」。<br />\n<br />\n坤哥日前同Cousin Fung出發去旅行，呢日嚟到巴黎鐵塔，坤哥成功同一班好青春嘅鬼妹合照，又指自己係「巴黎鐵搭訕」，自封「交際花坤」。<br />\n<br />\n從坤哥部分旅行照可見，佢穿上自己有份設計，寫住「Eat Good West」嘅自家製衛衣，可惜佢同鬼妹合照時，並非穿著呢件「食好西」衫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/58db010ba10e5e04d7868f3f7974ad8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F58db010ba10e5e04d7868f3f7974ad8e.png&h=56453730&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"322ca5fdcd01a056e7672ca91372cc2853288e9e","tid":550062,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"勁過KPOP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坤哥紅到去法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c642b3b4d23cf75e6b00390f1900f1c2b9eb3207","tid":550062,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"坤哥幾高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dafcacb8e8108302980920c19037f75bacd7fa","tid":550062,"uid":156138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坤哥幾高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啲鬼妹細粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}